Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
This property is located on the corner of Queens Road and Harris Road, Five Dock.

Approximately 410sqm located on the 2nd level this suite provides ample natural sunlight and balcony with western aspect.

Location:
Five Dock is a suburb in the inner-west of Sydney. The subject property is located 10 kilometres west of the Sydney Central Business District, 10 kilometres from the Parramatta CBD and 2.5 kilometres east of the entrance to the M4 Motorway, in the Local Government Area of the City of Canada Bay.

Five Dock lies between Parramatta Road and the City West Link to the south and Hen and Chicken Bay, on the Parramatta River, along with the suburbs of Wareemba and Russell Lea, to the north.

Five Dock is an increasingly popular suburb offering spectacular views to the city to which it is linked by both roads and ferry.
The subject building is located on the high profile corner of Queens Road and Harris Road, directly opposite Rosebank College High School. This is an extremely busy intersection as Queens Road is an important alternate route to Parramatta Road for both east and west bound traffic. There is undercover parking within the building with access off Harris Road and with Five Dock's close proximity to the CBD the site is serviced by public buses, with a stop directly in front of the building.

CBRE is pleased to present 73-77 Ramsay Road, Five Dock to the market for sale first time offered in 40 years.

The property a two-storey mixed use building asset positioned at the heart of Five Dock retail town centre with exceptional vehicular and foot traffic exposure along Great North Road. The property’s address and title identify a frontage facing Ramsay Road however, the property’s exposure extends around the corner with seven retail spaces fronting the busiest intersection at Five Dock. Known as the Cashman’s Corner, the property by itself represents a corner site both for value add as well as potential redevelopment (STCA).

73-77 Ramsay Road, Five Dock benefits from the following attributes;

- Almost fully leased freehold building presenting an opportunity to invest or occupy
- Currently a two-storey mixed-use building let to 14 tenants across 16 tenancies
- Annual net passing income of $274,826.25*
- Prime positioning at the heart of Five Dock retail strip
- Prominent corner site with dual street frontages
*approximate
